1
00:01:31,240 --> 00:01:32,600
My hand hurts so much.

2
00:01:32,640 --> 00:01:33,600
I made an emergency appointment.

3
00:01:33,600 --> 00:01:35,039
Can you take me there?

4
00:01:38,080 --> 00:01:38,720
Lu Fan.

5
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:44,080
What happened to you?

6
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:45,880
I'm fine.

7
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:48,200
Let me see.

8
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:54,289
Let me take you to the hospital.

9
00:01:55,440 --> 00:01:56,080
Let's go.

10
00:01:59,360 --> 00:02:00,240
Stay away!

11
00:02:06,880 --> 00:02:08,039
Stay away from me!

12
00:02:10,440 --> 00:02:11,560
I was wrong.

13
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:14,840
I'm the one who got Brother Lu Fan hurt.

14
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,160
It's my fault.

15
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:18,200
But...

16
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:20,520
I also tried to save him.

17
00:02:21,320 --> 00:02:23,250
I also went to deliver the message.

18
00:02:26,320 --> 00:02:28,040
I really know I was wrong.

19
00:02:28,040 --> 00:02:29,079
I know I was wrong.

20
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:30,520
Don't come over!

21
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:32,360
Stay away!

22
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:37,480
Xia!

23
00:02:39,320 --> 00:02:41,920
Do you realize what you‘re doing?

24
00:02:43,160 --> 00:02:44,440
It's kidnapping.

25
00:02:44,880 --> 00:02:46,200
This is a crime!

26
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:47,840
If you don't talk,

27
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:49,680
we'll take you to the police station.

28
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:51,200
Xia, just say it.

29
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:53,360
Fine.

30
00:02:53,480 --> 00:02:54,560
You won't talk, huh?

31
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:56,820
We're taking you to the police! Let's go!

32
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:57,720
Let's go!

33
00:02:58,160 --> 00:02:59,840
Xia!

34
00:02:59,880 --> 00:03:01,920
Are you going to talk or not?

35
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:04,520
Are you?

36
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:06,000
Tell us!

37
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:07,480
Who is it? Tell us!

38
00:03:08,920 --> 00:03:10,580
I'll take her to the dark room.

39
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:11,760
Let's go!

40
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:12,840
No!

41
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:15,170
I don't want to go to the dark room,
Sister!

42
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:18,579
Are you going to the dark room
or the police station?

43
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:20,440
Let's go!

44
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:22,160
Sister, help! Sister!

45
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:22,800
Move!

46
00:04:04,200 --> 00:04:04,920
Hello.

47
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:07,920
The number you dialed cannot be reached.

48
00:04:32,159 --> 00:04:32,880
Hello.

49
00:04:33,200 --> 00:04:35,800
The number you dialed cannot be reached.

50
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:43,240
How is it?

51
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,520
How do you feel?

52
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,970
Did this underground tranquility

53
00:04:50,159 --> 00:04:52,080
remind you of the past?

54
00:04:54,200 --> 00:04:54,880
Lu Fan,

55
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,400
you're quite something.

56
00:04:58,080 --> 00:04:59,000
You won.

57
00:04:59,640 --> 00:05:00,280
No,

58
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:01,600
not yet.

59
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:07,320
I'm still too gentle.

60
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:11,480
Xiao Qi taught me
a hard lesson last night.

61
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,840
He said he never threatens anyone,

62
00:05:13,840 --> 00:05:15,000
especially women.

63
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:16,560
See?

64
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:19,280
I changed the way I play right away.

65
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,260
Actually, last night,

66
00:05:31,080 --> 00:05:32,920
I figured something out.

67
00:05:36,840 --> 00:05:37,920
About Xiao Qi.

68
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:42,400
About why he dug up my mother's grave

69
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:44,240
and scattered her ashes.

70
00:05:46,400 --> 00:05:48,520
Because he wanted to distract me.

71
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:52,000
He wanted to use the most extreme method

72
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:54,600
to make me direct all my hatred

73
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:55,840
and all my anger

74
00:05:56,280 --> 00:05:58,640
solely on him.

75
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,800
He used my mother's ashes

76
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:03,520
to pave the way for you.

77
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,400
He wanted me to let you go.

78
00:06:08,520 --> 00:06:09,520
But I won't.

79
00:06:11,840 --> 00:06:13,500
I won't give him what he wants.

80
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:18,200
I don't understand what you're saying.

81
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:22,720
These things have nothing to do with me.

82
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:23,800
Good.

83
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:27,730
Remember what you said.

84
00:06:29,280 --> 00:06:30,940
Do what you're supposed to do.

85
00:06:43,840 --> 00:06:45,360
This is your last chance.

86
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:49,640
Brother,

87
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,500
have you ever loved me?

88
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:26,160
Get up.

89
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:27,880
Get up!

90
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:44,560
Come on!

91
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:46,480
Come on!

92
00:07:57,960 --> 00:07:59,020
How do you feel now?

93
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:00,680
Much better.

94
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:03,560
Thank you for staying with me last night.

95
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,680
I'm really fine now.

96
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:12,480
This is...

97
00:08:13,760 --> 00:08:14,560
You're here?

98
00:08:17,280 --> 00:08:17,960
Look.

99
00:08:18,200 --> 00:08:19,930
This suits your status better.

100
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:21,850
Do you feel wronged?

101
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,370
What can I do for you?

102
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:26,400
You haven't eaten since yesterday, right?

103
00:08:27,760 --> 00:08:28,620
Are you hungry?

104
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:31,280
Squat down.

105
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:16,760
You try it too.

106
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:24,600
Come on,

107
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:26,290
open your mouth.

108
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:35,400
Open your mouth and eat!

109
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:46,760
Eat.

110
00:10:04,960 --> 00:10:05,560
Good shot.

111
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:11,880
Xiao Qi,

112
00:10:12,680 --> 00:10:14,210
your plan is not going well.

113
00:10:15,280 --> 00:10:17,840
If the Jian family doesn't step in,
I can't help you.

114
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:20,100
You might as well talk to the Jian family.

115
00:10:23,160 --> 00:10:23,880
Mr. Zhao,

116
00:10:24,680 --> 00:10:27,080
before Lu Fan and the Jian family
fall out,

117
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:29,200
it's inappropriate for me to contact them.

118
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:30,600
But don't worry, Mr. Zhao.

119
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:31,600
I have my own pace.

120
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,080
No matter what,

121
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:41,210
in the end, the profits of the Lu family
must belong to me.

122
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:43,560
I still have some things to do abroad,

123
00:10:43,560 --> 00:10:45,160
so I'm going back for a while.

124
00:10:45,760 --> 00:10:46,720
During this time,

125
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:49,680
you can contact my granddaughter,
Zhao Yuan.

126
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:55,010
Mr. Zhao,
I'll let you know when I'm ready.

127
00:10:57,720 --> 00:11:00,320
Aren't you going to give it a try
with Zhao Yuan?

128
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:02,160
She has always liked you.

129
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:04,880
Mr. Zhao, you know me.

130
00:11:04,880 --> 00:11:05,440
Regarding this aspect...

131
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:06,500
Alright, alright.

132
00:11:07,760 --> 00:11:09,090
Young people can decide

133
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:11,730
these kinds of things for themselves.

134
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:18,850
Where is she?

135
00:11:20,040 --> 00:11:20,600
She...

136
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:24,220
She probably went to find Xiao Qi.

137
00:11:30,400 --> 00:11:31,200
Good.

138
00:11:33,400 --> 00:11:34,260
Where are they?

139
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:36,560
Probably...

140
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,040
Probably?

141
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:44,170
Where are the guys tailing him?

142
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:45,320
They lost him.

143
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:48,720
Useless fools.

144
00:11:51,640 --> 00:11:52,680
Go find them!

145
00:11:52,880 --> 00:11:53,560
Yes.

146
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:54,400
Yes, Mr. Lu.

147
00:12:00,800 --> 00:12:01,680
Xiao Qi.

148
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:17,640
Why?

149
00:12:19,160 --> 00:12:20,320
Why did you do that?

150
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:26,240
I just didn't want you

151
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:28,240
to get tangled up in this cemetery issue

152
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:29,200
for too long.

153
00:12:30,520 --> 00:12:32,280
This wasn't in our plan at all.

154
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:45,930
These are Lu Fan's mother's ashes.

155
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:47,440
Give them to him.

156
00:12:47,760 --> 00:12:48,520
His hatred towards you

157
00:12:48,520 --> 00:12:50,160
has almost been vented.

158
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:52,760
I don't need to teach you what to do,
right?

159
00:12:52,760 --> 00:12:53,640
Xiao Qi.

160
00:12:56,560 --> 00:12:57,480
I'm tired.

161
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:04,600
But it's not over yet.

162
00:13:05,760 --> 00:13:07,040
It is all over.

163
00:13:07,920 --> 00:13:09,600
Our enemy has been punished.

164
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:11,130
The culprit has already...

165
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:12,360
No.

166
00:13:13,120 --> 00:13:14,160
It's not over.

167
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:16,490
The Lu family is still here,

168
00:13:17,800 --> 00:13:19,200
and they are not dead yet.

169
00:13:24,160 --> 00:13:24,960
Su Xia,

170
00:13:26,320 --> 00:13:27,760
no one can stop me.

171
00:13:28,640 --> 00:13:29,840
In this world,

172
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:31,450
only you understand me.

173
00:13:36,840 --> 00:13:38,600
Mr. Lu, Mr. Lu!

174
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:40,600
Please... Please give me
a little more time.

175
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:41,400
I...

176
00:13:41,400 --> 00:13:44,280
I will turn the whole city
upside down, Mr. Lu!

177
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:45,840
Mr. Lu...

178
00:13:46,240 --> 00:13:47,160
Mr. Lu!

179
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:50,200
Mr. Lu! Mr. Lu!

180
00:13:50,200 --> 00:13:51,240
I'm begging you!

181
00:13:51,240 --> 00:13:53,640
Please give me one more chance, Mr. Lu!

182
00:13:53,720 --> 00:13:56,000
Give me one more chance!

183
00:13:58,640 --> 00:13:59,440
Five hours.

184
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:03,690
If you can't find her in 5 hours,

185
00:14:04,480 --> 00:14:05,740
you'll end up like him.

186
00:14:06,320 --> 00:14:07,040
Mr. Lu,

187
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:09,320
you still have leverage over Ms. Su.

188
00:14:09,560 --> 00:14:11,280
She definitely won't leave. She is just...

189
00:14:11,280 --> 00:14:13,960
You have 4 hours and 59 minutes left.

190
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:25,960
Su Xia.

191
00:14:27,640 --> 00:14:29,640
Go. It's almost over.

192
00:14:34,520 --> 00:14:35,320
Wait.

193
00:14:41,800 --> 00:14:42,760
I told you

194
00:14:42,960 --> 00:14:44,320
I'd let you handle it

195
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:45,640
in your own way.

196
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:48,960
But if you go off course,

197
00:14:49,520 --> 00:14:51,080
I will put you back on track.

198
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:52,600
Xiao Qi.

199
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:53,640
Alright.

200
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:02,120
I trust you.

201
00:15:30,040 --> 00:15:32,920
Set up a meeting with Xiao Qi tomorrow.
